{"name":"Smart watches","category":"Electronics","price":3000,"stock":9,"brand":"watch","sku":"","shortDesc":"Earpods, also known as earbuds, are compact audio devices designed to fit comfortably inside the ear, delivering high-quality sound for music, calls, and media. They come in both wired and wireless (Bluetooth) versions, with modern wireless earpods offering seamless connectivity to smartphones, tablets, and laptops.\n\nMost earpods feature a sleek, lightweight design with soft silicone tips for a secure and comfortable fit, making them ideal for long listening sessions. Advanced models include features such as touch controls, noise cancellation, water resistance, and built-in microphones for clear voice calls.\n\nWireless earpods are typically paired with a portable charging case that not only stores them safely but also extends battery life, allowing multiple recharges on the go. They are especially popular for daily use, workouts, travel, and hands-free communication due to their convenience and portability.\n\nOverall, earpods combine style, functionality, and mobility, making them an essential accessory for modern digital lifestyles.","description":"Earpods, also known as earbuds, are compact audio devices designed to fit comfortably inside the ear, delivering high-quality sound for music, calls, and media. They come in both wired and wireless (Bluetooth) versions, with modern wireless earpods offering seamless connectivity to smartphones, tablets, and laptops.\n\nMost earpods feature a sleek, lightweight design with soft silicone tips for a secure and comfortable fit, making them ideal for long listening sessions. Advanced models include features such as touch controls, noise cancellation, water resistance, and built-in microphones for clear voice calls.\n\nWireless earpods are typically paired with a portable charging case that not only stores them safely but also extends battery life, allowing multiple recharges on the go. They are especially popular for daily use, workouts, travel, and hands-free communication due to their convenience and portability.\n\nOverall, earpods combine style, functionality, and mobility, making them an essential accessory for modern digital lifestyles.","featured":true,"images":["data:image/jpeg;base64,","data:image/jpeg;base64,"],"sellerId":"9ARCgweVg8wQ01vU","sellerName":"Iftikahar","_id":"DvV0C95CzQ6L0jOg","createdAt":{"$$date":1777308787780},"updatedAt":{"$$date":1777309194999}}
